Operator
The Operator is a technical genius who can build, repair, modify, and jury-rig
almost any vehicle, robot, or weapon system. On Rifts Earth, a good Operator
is worth their weight in plutonium.

Operators begin with the most comprehensive technical skill package of any OCC.
They choose from Technical, Science, Mechanical, Electrical, and Pilot Related
categories, giving them unmatched engineering versatility.

Attribute requirements: IQ 14.
Starting equipment: Full tool kit, portable diagnostics computer, personal
sidearm, work clothes, and a well-maintained vehicle.
